when laser pointers
were a novelty,

00:29:01.250 --> 00:29:02.780
they became all the
rage to put them

00:29:02.780 --> 00:29:05.960
right into your laser pointer.

00:29:05.960 --> 00:29:09.950
So here's another laser pointer.

00:29:09.950 --> 00:29:13.640
So here is a thing
that you screw

00:29:13.640 --> 00:29:17.660
in the end, which has a fraction
