00:31:15.150 --> 00:31:17.350
The way you can think
about diffraction grating,

00:31:17.350 --> 00:31:19.380
so now I want think about
a more general theory.

00:31:19.380 --> 00:31:21.240
I've worked out
a specific theory

00:31:21.240 --> 00:31:24.510
for a one-dimensional
diffraction grating,

00:31:24.510 --> 00:31:27.540
now I want to think
about the general theory.

00:31:27.540 --> 00:31:31.440
What if I simply told you
